[quote=“Anc13ntsIsBack, post:10, topic:407890”]Do you guys think Aliens(Not human\Mexicans, different planet) are real? A lot of people don’t for some reason. I think so considering the fact that there’s thousands of galaxy’s and planets.
OT: I do and don’t think the world will end in 2012, but I do think something will happen though. I’m not 100% about the “New World Order” but a lot of people do say their is a Government, within the Government, and that the Government hides a lot of things. Like, Spacecrafts from crashes and such. (Which I believe)
For Example:

[quote]The Atom Smasher

Scientists in Europe have been building the world’s largest particle accelerator. Basically its a 27km tunnel designed to smash atoms together to find out what makes the Universe tick. However, the mega-gadget has caused serious concern, with some scientists suggesting that it’s probably even a bad idea to turn it on in the first place. They’re predicting all manner of deadly results, including mini black holes. So when this machine is fired up for its first serious experiment in 2012, the world could be crushed into a super-dense blob the size of a basketball.
[/quote]
This, and how the “Poles” are said to be shifting.

In 2012 the next polar reversal will take place on earth. This means that the North Pole will be changed into the South Pole. Scientifically this can only be explained by the fact that the earth will start rotating in the opposite direction, together with a huge disaster of unknown proportions.

Those kind of things make me think it will\something may happen, due to all the Natural Disasters that have been happening.
even Norway is doing something about it: http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/science/nature/4605398.stm
But some other people I heard said,
Mayan Calander:
“The Mayan Calender is just an end of a cycle(But longer), like a regular calender each year.”

Also the thing about Judgement day, which didn’t happen which has been predicted 2 times so far.

I still think the world will end in 2012/something may happen. But I’m not going to go all out like some people do, which I read on some article that they sold everything and just had enough money till the year 2012, December 21st.[/quote]
First time ever, I agree with everything you said there.
All the alien sightings recently makes me think if they are planning on something. Even some rumors say that they are working with the goverment.
